	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I am level 52 now and have not used this at all for most of 6 levels.&nbsp;&nbsp;It is a wonderful weapon I have a pierce skill of 175 and it is due only to MOQ.  It is my belief that you should try to max all your skills.  Maxing all of your skills seems to me to make for a more well rounded character and a more fun game.<br><br>I used this mostly fighting in groups in High Pass Hold.  As long as you have a good group it is a great item to use the damage is excellent for the level and it is a fun weapon.  I now have all my other skills maxed.<br><br>I now use mostly Strength of Grogan.  41dmgm 51dly, +25str, +10sta nodrop.  I am working on my epic but it is a long haul.<br><br>Good Luck all<br>If you see me please say hi!<br>Remember if you need a rez at 50% they are always free from me<br><br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Fri Apr 12 01:11:37 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
