	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>For all you hundreds of Erudite paladins out there - starting about level 15 you can practice with this weapon on the sharks in Erudin harbor to improve your skill.&nbsp;&nbsp;(You can start as early as 9th but you will not get many hits in).<br><br>Go stand on the ledge in the water (you will be half in and half out of the water and will NOT be swimming or holding your breath) and fight the sharks.  When you are almost dead move up onto the land, heal yourself (via spell, lay hand, or just resting) then wade back into the water. <br><br>Lather - Rinse - Repeat.   It will take a while but there is NO chance of you dying.  <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
